## 2026-03-28 - `token-store.ts` uses `any` types pervasively for token group traversal
- Replaced all 22 `any` type annotations in `token-store.ts` with a local `TokenNode` type alias (`Record<string, unknown>`) and targeted `as TokenNode` casts after runtime type narrowing (`typeof x === 'object' && x !== null`).
