## 2026-03-28 - SSE connection (useServerEvents) never reconnects after server restart
- Added manual reconnection with exponential backoff (1s–30s) when EventSource enters CLOSED state
- Used a `callbackRef` pattern to avoid tearing down the connection when the `onGeneratorError` callback identity changes, removing it from the effect dependency array
- On `onerror`, if `readyState === CLOSED` (browser gave up auto-reconnect), manually schedule a new `EventSource` after a backoff delay; reset delay on successful `onopen`

