## 2026-03-28 - TokenEditor "toggle alias mode" doesn't preserve the resolved value
- Updated `handleToggleAlias` in TokenEditor to resolve the current alias reference via `resolveTokenValue` when switching from alias to direct mode, so the resolved concrete value (e.g. `#1a73e8`) is kept instead of reverting to the stale pre-alias raw value
- Falls back to pre-alias value if resolution fails (broken alias, not yet set, etc.)
- Files changed: `packages/figma-plugin/src/ui/components/TokenEditor.tsx` ~L13-14 (import), ~L342-363 (handleToggleAlias)

